# Copilot Credits Dashboard - Granting Admin Access

The [admin view](https://moj-copilot-ai-credits-dashboard-prod.cloud-platform.service.justice.gov.uk/admin) 
of the Copilot Credits Dashboard displays GitHub CoPilot cost data for all organisations in the
[Ministry of Justice (UK)](https://github.com/enterprises/ministry-of-justice-uk) enterprise
which have GitHub CoPilot enabled.

To grant users access to this view, users will need to be added to the [moj-copilot-credits-dashboard-admin](https://github.com/orgs/ministryofjustice/teams/moj-copilot-credits-dashboard-admin)
GitHub team.